167
00:18:21,136 --> 00:18:22,657
Meng Tong, you go home.

168
00:18:22,856 --> 00:18:24,017
Come on time tomorrow.

169
00:18:24,056 --> 00:18:24,657
Bye.

170
00:18:25,417 --> 00:18:26,177
