192
00:21:39,697 --> 00:21:41,497
It's okay.

193
00:21:44,776 --> 00:21:45,417
It's okay.

194
00:21:48,697 --> 00:21:49,776
Who are you?

195
00:21:50,136 --> 00:21:50,897
I'm

196
