to draw realistically.

199
00:22:20,257 --> 00:22:23,257
But to inspire them
to unlock their imagination

200
00:22:23,457 --> 00:22:25,056
and find their own style.

201
00:22:25,616 --> 00:22:27,336
Otherwise, at their age,

202
00:22:27,336 --> 00:22:28,937
they'd end up with improper imitation.

203
00:22:31,296 --> 00:22:34,336
Improper imitation?

204
00:22:36,136 --> 00:22:37,136
I remember a saying.

205
00:22:37,136 --> 00:22:39,657
It's difficult

206
00:22:40,096 --> 00:22:42,376
to draw common things well.

207
00:22:46,816 --> 00:22:47,417
Indeed.

208
00:22:48,737 --> 00:22:51,856
It's difficult to draw

209
00:22:51,977 --> 00:22:53,136
common things from life well.

210
00:22:53,296 --> 00:22:55,257
Because the slightest deviation

211
00:22:55,336 --> 00:22:56,296
gets noticed easily.

212
00:22:57,576 --> 00:22:58,897
You're absolutely right.

213
00:23:00,056 --> 00:23:02,536
It's difficult to imitate human.

214
00:23:03,897 --> 00:23:05,336
Even if one imitates perfectly,

215
00:23:05,856 --> 00:23:07,657
