226
00:24:52,457 --> 00:24:55,336
There's a birdwatching platform ahead.

227
00:24:55,856 --> 00:24:56,616
Quite noticeable.

228
00:24:57,296 --> 00:24:58,737
Drive a bit further forward, please.

229
00:25:00,257 --> 00:25:02,536
