in this pitch darkness?

230
00:25:04,017 --> 00:25:04,616
Listen.

231
00:25:05,497 --> 00:25:06,856
Can you hear the bird chirping?

232
00:25:08,096 --> 00:25:09,497
This is the bird we're looking for.

233
00:25:09,856 --> 00:25:10,536
What?

234
00:25:11,616 --> 00:25:12,616
