245
00:27:25,217 --> 00:27:26,096
Here!

246
00:27:26,497 --> 00:27:28,417
Help her onto that bench. Hurry!

247
00:27:30,257 --> 00:27:31,056
Easy, easy.

248
00:27:31,296 --> 00:27:32,336
Check on her.

249
00:27:32,336 --> 00:27:34,257
