257
00:27:43,737 --> 00:27:45,336
Did you get it? What took you so long?

258
00:27:45,737 --> 00:27:46,776
Go help him.

259
00:27:47,457 --> 00:27:47,977
I...

260
00:27:48,457 --> 00:27:49,296
Or you hold this.

261
00:27:49,296 --> 00:27:50,697
Hurry up, okay?

262
00:27:51,776 --> 00:27:54,096
Hurry up. It might be a severe wound.

263
00:27:54,096 --> 00:27:55,536
