275
00:29:01,977 --> 00:29:03,336
But she's got real grit.

276
00:29:03,737 --> 00:29:04,937
She was merciless on herself.

277
00:29:06,657 --> 00:29:07,457
We should go.

278
00:29:08,937 --> 00:29:10,536
Follow her to a safe place.

279
00:29:11,336 --> 00:29:12,017
Use my car.

280
00:29:15,017 --> 00:29:16,737
I checked it. It won't be tracked.

281
00:29:18,816 --> 00:29:19,417
Thanks.

282
00:29:20,296 --> 00:29:21,697
What about you?

283
00:29:21,776 --> 00:29:23,177
Ms. Lin will suspect you.

284
00:29:27,776 --> 00:29:29,737
