335
00:33:56,417 --> 00:33:57,457
Lin Ling might need

336
00:33:57,457 --> 00:33:58,856
to stay here for a while.

337
00:34:01,017 --> 00:34:02,776
Seems my place isn't a dumpling shop,

338
00:34:03,177 --> 00:34:05,217
but a Changxi Sanatorium.

339
00:34:06,536 --> 00:34:09,136
Every girl connected to Tuo

340
00:34:09,817 --> 00:34:11,417
gets sent here when injured.

341
00:34:12,616 --> 00:34:14,017
Where's Tuo?

342
00:34:18,056 --> 00:34:18,777
Yan Tuo...

343
00:34:20,576 --> 00:34:21,337
Tuo...

344
00:34:23,337 --> 00:34:23,977
He...

345
00:34:28,417 --> 00:34:30,377
