353
00:34:46,937 --> 00:34:47,897
And I won't ask further.

354
00:34:48,096 --> 00:34:48,616
Alright then.

355
00:34:48,817 --> 00:34:49,736
Just one thing.

356
00:34:50,297 --> 00:34:52,176
Don't do anything illegal.

357
00:34:52,696 --> 00:34:53,576
Don't worry.

358
00:34:54,216 --> 00:34:56,337
Don't you trust Yan Tuo?

359
00:34:58,136 --> 00:35:00,056
Alright, sit here for a bit.

360
00:35:00,337 --> 00:35:01,576
